<%# <h1>Guests#show</h1> %>
<div class="d-flex" style="position:relative">
  <span><p id="notice" style="position:absolute; top: 10px; right: 10px; background-color:rgb(165, 156, 148); color:black"><%= notice %></p></span>
  <div class="container m-0">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-3 sideImage">
      </div>
      <div class="col px-4 sideInfo">
        <h1 class="questions">Details & Questions</h1>
        <h2 class="questions">Virtual shower details:</h2>
        <p>
          Prepare your favorite tea or another drink to sip while we're together. If you want to try Janaya's favorite teas, check out these two:
          <a href="https://commoditeas.com/collections/all-teas/products/vanilla-rooibos">Vanilla Rooibos</a> and
          <a href="https://commoditeas.com/collections/all-teas/products/chai-tea">Chai</a>.
          <br><br>
          Dress to impress but still be comfortable. Most importantly, come prepared to have some fun!
          We'll play games and share stories and advice to prepare her for the little one!
        </p>
        <p style="font-weight:bold">We want to send a special gift to 10 people. Please <%= link_to "RSVP by Sunday, June 5th", new_guest_path %>
        to be included in the drawing!</p>
        <img id="tea" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1571934811356-5cc061b6821f?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2067&q=80" alt="china teacup full of tea with tea leaves all around">

        <h2 class="questions">Questions</h2>
          <h3 class="topic">...about the Shower</h3>
          <ul>
          <li>
          <p class="question"><i class="arrow down"></i> I can no longer attend. Can I update my RSVP?</p>
          <p><div class="my-3">
            <form action="/guests/:id/edit" method="get">
              <label for="phone_number">Enter your phone number (include dashes) to update your RSVP</label>
              <div>
              <input type="text" name="phone_number" placeholder="### - ### - ####" class="label">
              <input type="submit" value="RSVP", class="button" >
              </div>
            </form>
          </div></p>
          </li>
          <li>
          <p class="question"><i class="arrow down"></i> Is there a theme or dress code for the shower?</p>
          <p class="answer">It would be great if you dressed as if you were joining us in person. A beautiful, comfortable, summer dress would be perfect!
          </p>
          </li>
          <li>
          <p class="question"><i class="arrow down"></i> What colors would they like for gifts?</p>
          <p class="answer">We love autumn tones - beige, burgundy, teal, forest green. Think of a beautiful fall day!<br>
          </p>
          <div id="colors" class="d-flex justify-content-around" style="width:300px">
            <span id="beige"></span>
            <span id="red"></span>
            <span id="teal"></span>
            <span id="green"></span>
            <span id="blue"></span>
          </div>
          </li>
          <li>
          <p class="question"><i class="arrow down"></i> Can I send money instead of buying a gift?</p>
          <p class="answer">Yes, you can send to $jnygrppr with <a href="https://cash.app/$jnygrppr">CashApp</a>.</p>
          </li>
          </ul>
          <h3 class="topic">...about the Baby</h3>
          <ul>
          <li>
          <p class="question"><i class="arrow down"></i> Do they know the gender?</p>
          <p class="answer">Not yet, it will be a surprise! If you want to find out on the day of the birth, let us know on your RSVP.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p class="question"><i class="arrow down"></i> Do they want a boy or a girl?</p>
            <div>
              <%# <img id="hair" src="https://www.voice-online.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/GettyImages-169327593.jpg" alt=""> %>
              <p class="answer">Janaya is not sure she can handle a full head of hair, so she'd love to have a boy! Nate is ready for either!</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
          <p class="question"><i class="arrow down"></i> What is the due date?</p>
          <p class="answer">The little one is expected to arrive on June 22nd!</p>
          </li>
          <li>
          <p class="question"><i class="arrow down"></i> Have they chosen a name?</p>
          <p class="answer">Not yet. It's the hardest thing - we welcome suggestions!!</p>
          </li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="topic">...about the Parents-to-be</h3>
          <ul>
          <li>
          <p class="question"><i class="arrow down"></i> What does SHE need the most?</p>
          <p class="answer">If you could order sleep, that's her first choice.. Since it's hard to find, buy her donuts, dumplings, or any dish with
          an UberEats giftcard! <a href="https://about.ubereats.com/ca/en/how-it-works/uber-eats-gift-card/">Click here for UberEats Canada.</a></p>
          </li>
          <li>
          <p class="question"><i class="arrow down"></i> What does HE need the most?</p>
          <p class="answer">Coffee! If you'd like to order something special for the father,
           a gift card to his favorite cafe would make him smile. <a href="https://zabcafe.com/en/collections/carte-cadeau/products/carte-cadeau-zab-gift-card">Get one here!</a> </p>
          </li>
          </ul>
           <%# <script>
              const question = document.querySelectorAll("p.question")

              function changeDisplay(item) {
                const answer = item.nextElementSibling
                item.addEventListener("click", (event) => {
                console.log(event);
                console.log(event.currentTarget);
                if (answer.style.display === "none") {
                    answer.style.display = "block";
                    item.style.backgroundColor = "#FFFFFF";
                  } else {
                    answer.style.display = "none";
                    item.style.backgroundColor = "";
                  }
              })}
              question.forEach(changeDisplay);
            </script> %>
          <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
            <%= link_to "Home", root_path, class: "btn btn-light", style:"font-weight: bold; box-shadow: 2px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2)" %>
          </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
